{"tid":991063,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔知幾多手科技]LG V40賣建議零售價 $5998","createTime":"2019-01-22T06:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T01:00:17.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"747efe4361317aa754d9366430a83585c1a4dbaa","tid":991063,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"2019年用差唔多六千蚊買845<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAh Kwan 阿坤(prince1025) 2019-01-21 23:18<br />\n<br />\n由 2018 拖到 2019 都未見影的 LG V40 ThinQ，終於有賣價同上市日嘅消息了！而豐澤亦都已在 Facebook 專頁發帖，宣布呢部 V40 ThinQ 現已接受預訂，而且預訂仲有嘢送𠻹！如果網友對呢部 V40 ThinQ 有興趣，就要留意以下六點！<br />\n<br />\n001：LG V40 ThinQ 在 25/1 上市，現已在大舖接受預訂。<br />\n<br />\n002：建議零售價 $5998。<br />\n<br />\n003：有藍、紅兩種顏色。<br />\n<br />\n004：預訂送<br />\n- 6 個月屏幕保養 / 64GB MicroSD 咭 / 10,000mAh 流動充電器 (三選一)<br />\n- V40ThinQ贈品套裝<br />\n- 額外1年本地保養<br />\n<br />\n005：Citi 信用卡享高達 $250簽賬回贈<br />\n<br />\n006：具有 6.4 吋 OLED 芒，香港版配備 S845 處理器，內置 6GB RAM 以及 128GB ROM，電池容量 3300mAh，有 3 個主鏡頭 + 2 個前置鏡頭，支援 MERIDIAN 調音技術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4531/212226/1/rv/lg-v40-thinq-launch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4531%2F212226%2F1%2Frv%2Flg-v40-thinq-launch%2F&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIpxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a43596e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4531/212226/1/rv/lg-v40-thinq-launch/</a>"},{"pid":"9afafd7b23104355d33cb9adec1156520e38df66","tid":991063,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5526bf0715483ed21ecbf309c0d8b02517b0213","tid":991063,"uid":83668,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"LG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src